title: Cosson (E)
body: E: Catalog of the plants collected by G. Mandon in 1865 and 1866 on the islands of Madeira and Porto Santo. (Bull. de la Soc. Bot. de France, vol. XV, 1868).

Madeira: Island where the mentioned plants were collected.

G. Mandon: Person responsible for collecting the plants in 1865 and 1866.

1865: Year in which the mentioned plants were collected.
1866: Year in which the mentioned plants were collected.
